window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>More than 2.7 million Weenies sold! Don't be a weenie. Listen to these stories. If you dare! </p> <p><i>Strikeout of the Bleacher Weenies</i> is the eighth collection of spooky short stories for ages 8 to 12 by popular author David Lubar. This is the perfect pick for young listeners who like a few chills and a lot of laughs.</p> <p>Welcome to the Weenie Zone! Here are 30 hilarious and harrowing stories that will scare you, make you laugh, or get you to see the world in a whole new way. Find out where the author got the idea for each story at the end of the book.</p>"; 
